high_descs: Turn around to face the sink.
Pull a bowl out from underneath the sink.
Rinse the bowl in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn left, hanging another left around the kitchen island to reach the shelf in the corner of the room.
Set the bowl down on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bowl to put on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the sink
Open the cabinet below the sink and remove the dirty bowl
Walk slightly left sink then turn back to face the sink
Wash the bowl under water in the sink then remove it
Turn around and walk forward then turn right to face the wooden shelf
Put the bowl on the middle shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the washed bowl on the wooden shelf

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink by the window.
Open the lower cabinets under the sink, pick up the dirty pan inside and close the doors.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the pan inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the rack of wooden shelves to the right.
Put the clean pan on the right side of the middle shelf on the rack.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan on a shelf.
